name: PRE ORDER -JAN- White Baseball Jersey Tshirt - FREE DELIVERY
description:
--------------------------------------
RERELEASE FOR 2014 - JANUARY DISPATCH - 
--------------------------------------

This design is based around American Baseball pinstripe fashion.

with full coverage over the whole tshirt white blue lining. 

This pattern is covered over the whole garment front and back and is a nicely fitted . 

** Please note ** 
All the 09 first 500 sales have been done so future white purchases will be without 09 on the back

65% polyester 
35% cotton 

T-shirt printed in Britain.

Available in all sizes and all deliveries would be between 14days as self production at the moment until I can employ staff! 

Small (chest size 34-36in)
Medium (38-40in)
Large (42-44in)
Extra Large (44-46in)

This is the first of the series and more colours to follow!


-style history

I did a lot of research on american baseball jerseys for example, New York Yankees, Boston Redsox, Pirates, Philly and how they are presented, and it seemed to be that there was only the basic Jersey shirts which was buttoned shirts usually found in a silk or a high density cotton.

My Idea was to not follow that trend and create a tshirt of style which could be warn out or as a casual tshirt. thinker pinstripe lining in a variation of colours and also a replica Red and blue sports badge attached at the bottom of the garment.

The fitting of the tshirt was a key so it could be based on unisex style and also rocked in different ways if people prefer longer tshirts but keeping arms slightly less loose. 

Sublimation will not cover across the whole sleeve as production width is not scaled across the whole tshirt, when bigger sizes are order, more white shown but great to roll sleeves with.
Creases may occur within the T-shirt print from Sublimation and cannot be helped. if purchased and received a particularly bad print send pictures through to me and I can try give a solution.
